sorcer.core.provider

Interface Provider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.jini.admin.Administrable, AnalyticsProducer, Exerter, Monitorable, java.rmi.Remote, Service
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SorcerNotifierProtocol
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdderDBProvider, AdderProvider, DatabaseProvider, ExertMonitor, IpcArrayProviderImpl, ServiceCataloger, ServiceProvider, ServiceTasker, SessionBeanProvider, SysCallerProvider, WorkerProvider

    public interface Provider
extends Service, Exerter, Monitorable, AnalyticsProducer, net.jini.admin.Administrable, java.rmi.Remote
    This is an interface that defines how a provider interacts with other code the through the methods that are exposed. It extends Service, Monitorable, and Remote.
    See Also:
    Service, Monitorable, Remote
